  m_Name: 40_Simulation
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  chapter: 10
  number: 40
  title: Hot Air Balloon
  description: "Experience how temperature differences create lift in a hot air balloon!
    In this simulation, you must manage the balloon\u2019s internal temperature to
    control its altitude and stay stable while flying above volatile volcanic terrain."
  objectives: 'Understand how heated air inside the balloon produces lift compared
    to the cooler ambient air.


    Learn to balance temperature and lift to maintain
    stable flight.


    Apply concepts of buoyancy and convection in real-time simulation.'
  scoring: 
  bronzeObjective: 
  silverObjective: 
  goldObjective: 
  timeBonus:
    timeBonuses: []
    lowestScore: 10
  unlockDatas:
  - icon: 3
    name: Level 41 - Challenge
    description: Volcanic Upsurge
  - icon: 2
    name: Freeplay > Simulation 10
    description: Hot Air Balloon
  instructions: '1. Use the up arrow to increase heat and down arrow to release it.


    2.
    Monitor the Hot Air Balloon Status panel for temperature, lift, and altitude
    changes.


    3. Keep the balloon stable and avoid overheating while navigating
    through turbulent air currents.


    4. Press End Simulation to finish your
    run.


    Note: The simulation ends if the balloon becomes unstable due to overheating
    or if lift force drops to zero, causing it to fall. Successfully maintain stable
    flight for the set duration while managing temperature and altitude efficiently.'
